To fix the Command Injection vulnerability in the given Java code snippet, we need to properly sanitize and validate the user input before executing it as a command. One way to achieve this is by using `ProcessBuilder` class instead of `Runtime.exec()` method.

Here is the fixed version of the code that includes proper security measures:

